              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <h3 class="color-green">OUR STORY</h3>
                <h2 class="color-green">MissMoo Plant-based Milks</h2>
                <p class="color-green">Actually started as MissMoo leites vegetais(Portuguese) in 2016.</p>
                <p class="color-green">Since then we've had some changes and growth, but we still love helping spread veganism with yummy food and beverages.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <h2 class="mobile-top color-green">WHY VEGANISM?</h2>
                <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">

                  <div class="panel panel-default" id="panel1">
                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingOne">
                      <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                          Very Quick Response
                        </a>
                      </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">
                      <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>Cause sentient beings are not ours to profit from, entertain ourselves, eat, run tests on, or dress ourselves with.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="panel panel-default" id="panel2">
                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingTwo">
                      <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                          Health
                        </a>
                      </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwo">
                      <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>Humans are ominvores and therefore do not have a biological need to consume animal products. In fact, we are far healthier when we adopt plant-based alternatives.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="panel panel-default" id="panel3">
                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingThree">
                      <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                          Ecosystems
                        </a>
                      </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree">
                      <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>The ecosystems of this planet we live on are under constant threat because of the choice to dedicate so many resources to the continuation of animal exploitation</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-12">
                <h3 class="wow bounceIn color-yellow text-center">Per day, as a vegan, you save:</h3>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-6">
                <div class="about-fact border-right">
